                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Augusta Ga.</placeName>\n                <date>21st Apr. 5626</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Since my last, the “Occident,” from<lb/> the commencement of the\n                present volume, has reached<lb/> me by mail. In the <date>June</date> No. I notice\n                some very<lb/> kind remarks about me, which claim my earnest<lb/> thanks.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have obtained two more subscribers<lb/> from <persName>Mrs\n                    Mordercai Hyams</persName> &amp; <persName>Mr Morris Cohen</persName>, to<lb/>\n                whom please forward the Nos. from No. 1 of the current year.<lb/> I shall continue\n                my endeavors to promote the circulation<lb/> of the Occident in this city,\n                    <del>the</del> but I apprehend I have<lb/> pretty much touched the limits.\n                Possibly I may yet be<lb/> able to influence one or two more.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am laboring diligently in the little<lb/> field in which I now\n                find myself, where I must confess<lb/> I do not find Religion or Knowing as I could\n                desire. Mam-<lb/>mon has stronger claims, &amp; greater influence than\n                    <sic>Adonay</sic>.<lb/> “'Tis true 'tis pity, and pity 'tis 'tis true.”Again, I\n                perceive<lb/> a tendency among several to go astray after the strange god,<lb/>\n                which you have characteristically termed “the modern hybrid,”</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pn8xx8x/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
