                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pn8xx8x/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>but as long as I remain here, I am determined it shall<lb/> make no headway, by\n                following the simple rule. Withstand<lb/> at the beginning. This for your uneducated\n                eye. Our<lb/> friend of the Messenger went a step too far in publishing<lb/> a\n                private letter to him, which annoyed me a little, tho<lb/> the matter was hardly\n                worth notice. At the breaking out<lb/> of the War, he became so political and\n                violent in his crusade against<lb/> the <placeName>South</placeName> that I\n                abandoned the agency of the paper and<lb/> even my continuance as a subscriber in a\n                letter which<lb/> was rather caustic. With the return of peace, I wished to<lb/>\n                remit him the subscription which I owed, and at same<lb/> time to introduce a\n                gentleman from <placeName>Augusta</placeName> who <del>wished</del><lb/> required\n                some Tallethoth, and whilst doing so, in the <sic>fulness</sic><lb/> of my heart,\n                and in deference to his years and long services<lb/> I held out freely the olive\n                branch. He ought to have drawn<lb/> the deliberate line of demarcation between this,\n                and the<lb/> topics I added on general Jewish making here. However<lb/>\n                <add>מה שעבר עבר</add> It is hardly worth notice indeed.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">With kind regards, participated in<lb/> by <persName>Mrs\n                    Jacobs</persName>, believe me</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">yours faithfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Henry S. Jacobs</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pn8xx8x/canvas/p2"
